[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0069","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0418","title":"Sendmail SMTP 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"该漏洞存在于 SMTP 服务器（如 Sendmail）中，远程攻击者可在同一连接中发送大量 RCPT TO 命令，耗尽服务器资源导致拒绝服务。攻击无需身份认证，仅需能连接目标 SMTP 端口（通常为 25/TCP）。影响运行 Sendmail 等 SMTP 软件的主机，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0418"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，该版本引入了连接限制机制。在 sendmail.cf 中设置 MaxRecipientsPerMessage=N（如 100）限制单次 SMTP 连接的 RCPT TO 数量。同时配置 access 文件拒绝来源异常的发件 IP，或在 MTA 层面启用 rate limiting 限制同一来源的并发连接数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92100018214316&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0069.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0057","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0411","title":"SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 启动脚本符号链接攻击本地提权漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 5.0.4p 版本的多个启动脚本（包括 S84rpcinit、S95nis、S85tcp、S89nfs）存在符号链接攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接，利用系统启动脚本在处理临时文件时的权限提升缺陷，在脚本以 root 权限执行时覆盖或篡改系统关键文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer Enterprise System 5.0.4p 及可能的相关版本，需要本地访问权限方能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0411"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-07","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.400","remediation":"建议升级至 SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 及以上版本（若厂商已发布补丁）；由于 SCO OpenServer 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。临时缓解措施：修改受影响启动脚本（S84rpcinit、S95nis、S85tcp、S89nfs）中临时文件的创建方式，使用 mktemp 替代直接写入 /tmp 目录，并将脚本文件权限设置为 root 可写（chmod 700），同时定期审计 /tmp 目录中的异常符号链接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0411","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0411"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0055","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0410","title":"Sun Solaris cancel 命令本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中 cancel 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该漏洞存在于 Solaris 7.0 及 Solaris 2.6 (i386) 版本中。本地攻击者可通过向 cancel 命令发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用该漏洞可获得 root 权限。由于攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，该漏洞的利用门槛较低，危害等级为高危（CVSS 7.2）。受影响的系统包括 Solaris 7.0 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0410"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.253","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-01 (x86) 或 105400-01 (SPARC)，或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：移除 cancel 命令的 setuid root 权限 (chmod 755 /usr/bin/cancel)，或限制受信用户访问该命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/293","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19234","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0410","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0410.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r9mp-gf5j-985f/GHSA-r9mp-gf5j-985f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0410.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d0c16ada-3ed0-423a-99c8-dc346abdf212.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0054","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0054.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0409","title":"SuSE Linux gnuplot 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 系统中 gnuplot 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 gnuplot 在处理特定输入时未对数据长度进行充分检查，导致本地用户可通过向程序提交特制超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据，实现权限提升获取 root 权限。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用。该漏洞影响 S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 等早期 Linux 发行版。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0409"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.127","remediation":"立即执行 `chmod -s /usr/bin/gnuplot` 移除 gnuplot 的 suid root 权限位，这是最直接有效的缓解措施。同时将 gnuplot 升级至 3.7 及以上版本，该版本已修复 plot.c 中 HOME 环境变量的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。如使用 S.u.S.E 系统，可将 `/etc/rc.config` 中 `PERMISSION_SECURITY` 设为 `\"paranoid\"` 以自动管理 suid 权限。作为深度防御，建议限制普通用户对 svgalib 和 /dev/mem 的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/319","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19254","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0409","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0409.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g722-hhhg-4rh7/GHSA-g722-hhhg-4rh7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0409.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0054.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1256","title":"Oracle Database Assistant 明文密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"Oracle Database Assistant 1.0 在 Oracle 8.0.3 Enterprise Edition 中创建新数据库时，会将数据库主密码以明文形式写入 spoolmain.log 日志文件。本地攻击者只需读取该日志文件即可获取数据库主密码，进而获得对数据库的未授权访问权限，可能导致敏感数据泄露。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需特殊权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1256"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Oracle 8.1.5（Oracle 8i）及以上版本以修复此漏洞。如暂时无法升级，创建数据库后立即删除或安全清除 %ORACLE_HOME%\\database\\spoolmain.log 文件，并将日志目录的访问权限设置为仅允许数据库管理员读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T09:48:50.911274894+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0221","title":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 150 端口（远程管理端口）发送特制数据包，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend 系列路由器，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中危。官方已发布固件更新修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0221"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.547","remediation":"在防火墙或访问控制列表（ACL）中限制对 TCP/UDP 150 端口的访问，仅允许 trusted 管理 IP 连接。如无需远程管理功能，建议在路由器配置中禁用远程管理服务（no remote-management）。若设备仍在使用，应升级至供应商支持的最新固件版本，或替换为受支持的现代路由器设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0221.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80896/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0222","title":"Cisco IOS Web Server 长URL拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 路由器的 Web 服务器组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标设备发送超长 URL 即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致 IOS 进程崩溃并迫使路由器重新启动，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响启用 HTTP 服务的 Cisco IOS 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。缓解措施为禁用不必要的 HTTP 服务或通过访问控制列表限制来源 IP。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0222"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.680","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复版本（如 11.2(18)、12.0(11) 及以上），或禁用 HTTP 服务：全局配置模式下执行 `no ip http server`。如需保留 HTTP 服务，通过 `ip http access-class` 配合 ACL 限制可信管理源地址，并在接口上应用 `ip access-group` 过滤对 80 端口的非授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/60159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0222","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0013","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0223","title":"Sun Solaris syslogd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 syslogd 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，当远程主机向目标 Solaris 系统发送 syslog 消息时，若该主机缺少反向 DNS（PTR）记录，syslogd 在处理过程中会发生崩溃，导致系统日志服务中断。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，持续发送此类消息可使 syslogd 反复崩溃，影响系统日志记录功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0223"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.797","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至包含此补丁的版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上），或在 /etc/syslog.conf 中禁用反向 DNS 解析功能；同时建议在防火墙层面限制外部主机向 UDP 514 端口发送 syslog 消息，防止未授权来源触发崩溃。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.Sun.COM/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?patchid=103291&collection=fpatches","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1878"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0261","title":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 服务存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于对 HELO 和 HELP 等 SMTP 命令输入长度缺乏有效边界检查。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 SMTP 端口发送超长命令（如 HELO 后跟超过 471 字符的主机名），触发缓冲区溢出导致服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Chameleon 4.5 及 UnixLink 97 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0261"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.477","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Netmanage Chameleon 4.5 及 Unixlink 97 的 SMTPd 服务（Windows NT 平台），由于产品早已停止维护且厂商未发布补丁，建议升级迁移至受支持的 SMTP 服务器（如 Exchange Server、Postfix 等）。若暂时无法迁移，应在防火墙限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接；同时监控 SMTP 服务的异常崩溃日志以及时发现攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.insecure.org/sploits/netmanage.chameleon.overflows.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0261","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2387/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0038","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0038.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0386","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 1.0 及 4.0 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的非标准 URL 请求，突破路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 Personal Web Server 的 Windows 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0386"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.143","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Personal Web Server 更高版本，或改用 IIS 替代 FrontPage PWS 根除风险。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用非标准 URL 解析，并部署 URLScan 安全工具过滤 `../../` 等目录遍历字符，同时限制 WEB 目录执行权限为纯脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/111","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-010","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19753","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0386.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0386","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0386.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0386.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/951.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-frontpage.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mspws_dotdotdot.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0038.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0060","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0413","title":"SGI IRIX X Server 字体路径缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统 X Window System 服务器在处理字体路径时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的字体路径参数触发该漏洞，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限才能利用。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0413"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.670","remediation":"安装 SGI 安全公告 19990301-01-PX 提供的对应补丁，或升级到包含该修复的 IRIX 版本。鉴于 SGI 已停止运营且 IRIX 已终止支持多年，建议将仍在运行的 IRIX 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统；若无法迁移，应严格限制本地登录权限、最小化可访问 X 服务器的用户范围，并禁用不必要的 X 字体服务以降低利用面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0061","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0061.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0414","title":"Linux Kernel TCP 欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.36 之前版本的 TCP 协议栈存在盲欺骗漏洞。远程攻击者可在未完成完整 TCP 三次握手前，通过预测 TCP 序列号向应用层注入伪造数据，绕过连接建立验证机制。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.30 至 2.0.37 版本，攻击者无需处于中间人位置即可实施盲注入攻击，可能导致数据篡改或会话劫持。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0414"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.800","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.0.36 或更高版本以修复 TCP 握手机制缺陷；若无法升级内核，启用 TCP syncookies（`echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/tcp_syncookies`）并配置 iptables 限制入站 TCP 连接速率以降低欺骗攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0414","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0414","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0414.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33wp-c8x6-pv3w/GHSA-33wp-c8x6-pv3w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000552.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0070","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0419","title":"Microsoft Exchange SMTP Service 4xx 错误代码拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 的 SMTP 服务在处理邮件投递时存在拒绝服务漏洞。当 SMTP 服务向目标邮件服务器发送邮件并收到 4xx 临时错误响应码时，会快速且反复地重试投递该邮件，导致系统资源被大量消耗，最终造成邮件服务不可用。攻击者可通过配置邮件服务器返回 4xx 状态码来触发此漏洞，影响 Exchange Server 的邮件处理功能。该漏洞属于早期发现的拒绝服务类问题，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0419"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.433","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该更新修复了 SMTP 服务在收到 4xx 错误码时陷入死循环导致拒绝服务的问题。临时缓解措施可在 SMTP 虚拟服务器上启用连接限制和超时设置，限制同一来源的并发连接数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0419","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0419","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0419.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3r6q-4vvg-jmx9/GHSA-3r6q-4vvg-jmx9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000553.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0079","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0426","title":"Linux Kernel /dev/kmem 默认权限不当导致 IP 欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.36 之前版本中 /dev/kmem 设备文件的默认权限设置不当，导致本地普通用户可读取内核内存空间。攻击者利用该漏洞可获取内核中的 TCP 序列号等敏感信息，进而实施盲 TCP 欺骗攻击，伪造 TCP 连接或破坏现有连接，影响系统通信安全。该漏洞无需特殊攻击条件，拥有本地账户即可利用，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0426"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.267","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.36 及以上版本，该版本修复了 /dev/kmem 默认权限问题。如无法升级内核，可将 /dev/kmem 权限修改为 640 或更严格，仅允许 root 用户读取，以降低 IP 欺骗攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0426","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19458","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0426.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0426","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0426.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vgr8-rhcx-42jv/GHSA-vgr8-rhcx-42jv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0426.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82490/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0079.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0086","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0086.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0429","title":"Lotus Notes 客户端加密邮件明文传输信息泄露漏洞","description":"Lotus Notes 4.5 客户端存在加密邮件明文传输漏洞。当用户发送加密邮件但未设置\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"首选项时，客户端会将加密邮件的副本以明文形式在网络上传输，导致加密保护失效。远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式捕获并读取本应加密的邮件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Lotus Notes 4.5 及可能的相关版本，攻击条件简单，只需攻击者处于同一网络段。官方建议用户启用\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"首选项以缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0429"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.620","remediation":"在 Lotus Notes 4.5 客户端中，依次进入\"文件→偏好设置→邮件\"，勾选\"Encrypt Saved Mail\"选项以强制加密已保存邮件。建议升级至 Lotus Notes 5.0 或更高版本，新版默认启用此安全选项。如无法升级，可在邮件服务器和客户端之间启用 SSL/TLS 加密传输作为额外缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92221437025743&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92241547418689&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92246997917866&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92249282302994&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0429","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0429.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-364x-96mf-p447/GHSA-364x-96mf-p447.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0429.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000554.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b240f787-e786-4698-8910-dd2f7ddf7